@namespace PgmStudio.Client.Pages.AuthoringParts

@* Landing / home screen (ND3) — where /authoring opens and the rail logo returns. A workspace with its
   own flow bar (phase = Import) walking three sub-steps: Source → Found → Plan.
   Source and Plan are panel-only (no central canvas); only Found previews the scanned world.
   (1) Source — open a local world folder now; a download-link field is shown but deferred (B8).
   (2) Found — the import brief the author confirms in the phases that follow.
   (3) Plan — the six-phase overview + Start. Replaces the old FlowSection. *@

<section class="ds-section" id="landing">
  <div class="ds-section-heading">
    <div>
      <p class="ds-kicker">Landing · home</p>
      <h2>Open a world, see what we found</h2>
    </div>
    <p>Where <code>/authoring</code> opens (and where the rail logo returns) — a workspace of its own,
       with a flow bar walking <strong>Source → Found → Plan</strong>. The studio scans a world
       (<strong>no <code>map.xml</code> needed</strong>), shows what it detected, then you start.</p>
  </div>

  <p class="ds-theming-note">
    The landing screen is the <strong>seed of the guidance model</strong>: it scans a terrain-only world and
    shows the <strong>"here's what we detected"</strong> brief — folder + files, the top-down render, the
    islands / symmetry / world-feature summary — which the author then <em>confirms</em> in World, Teams, etc.
    <strong>Now:</strong> <em>open a local folder</em> (region files, no xml) to validate the approach.
    <strong>Later:</strong> paste a <strong>download link</strong> and the studio fetches + imports the world
    (the <code>import-from-url</code> half of <code>B8</code>) — shown but deferred.
  </p>

  <div class="ds-steps">

  @* ── Sub-step 1 · Source (no central canvas) ────────────────────────────── *@
  <article class="ds-example">
    <div class="ds-example-label">Sub-step 1 of 3 — Source (open a folder now · from a link later, B8)</div>
    <div class="flow-bar">
      <div class="flow-bar-phase"><i data-lucide="import"></i><span>Import</span></div>
      <div class="flow-steps">
        <button class="flow-step flow-step--active">Source</button>
        <button class="flow-step">Found</button>
        <button class="flow-step">Plan</button>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-bar-actions">
        <button class="action-btn" disabled>Back</button>
        <button class="action-btn action-btn--primary"><i data-lucide="scan-search"></i> Scan &amp; continue</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ds-panel-frame">
      <div class="workspace-scroll">
        <section class="panel-section">
          <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
            <h2 class="section-title">Open a world folder</h2>
            <span class="badge badge--success">no xml needed</span>
          </div>
          <p class="section-desc">World folders under the maps roots with a <code>region/</code> but no
             <code>map.xml</code> — the new-map candidates. Pick one, or type a path.</p>
          <div class="panel-list">
            <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--selected"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="folder-open"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">thunder_blank</span><span class="list-tag">12 region files · 2.4 MB</span><span class="badge badge--success">selected</span></div>
            <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="folder"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">annealing_iv_blank</span><span class="list-tag">9 region files</span></div>
            <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="folder"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">outback_edition_blank</span><span class="list-tag">15 region files</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" style="margin-top:var(--space-3)">
            <label class="field-label">…or a folder path</label>
            <div class="ctrl-row">
              <input class="field-input" type="text" value="/maps/thunder_blank" />
              <button class="action-btn"><i data-lucide="folder-search"></i> Browse</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="section-footer">
            <span class="panel-save-status"><code>thunder_blank</code> · 12 <code>.mca</code> · <code>level.dat</code> present · <strong>no <code>map.xml</code></strong> — Scan &amp; continue to read it</span>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="panel-section">
          <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
            <h2 class="section-title">From a download link</h2>
            <span class="badge badge--dim">soon · B8</span>
          </div>
          <p class="section-desc">Paste an Overcast / S3 <code>//download</code> zip link; the studio fetches
             and imports the world. Deferred — the field shows the source, integration lands with
             <code>B8</code>.</p>
          <div class="field">
            <label class="field-label">Download URL</label>
            <input class="field-input" type="text" placeholder="https://…/maps/thunder/download" disabled />
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  @* ── Sub-step 2 · Found (the only sub-step with a canvas) ────────────────── *@
  <article class="ds-example">
    <div class="ds-example-label">Sub-step 2 of 3 — Found (the import brief — what the next phases confirm)</div>
    <div class="flow-bar">
      <div class="flow-bar-phase"><i data-lucide="import"></i><span>Import</span></div>
      <div class="flow-steps">
        <button class="flow-step flow-step--done"><i data-lucide="check"></i>Source</button>
        <button class="flow-step flow-step--active">Found</button>
        <button class="flow-step">Plan</button>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-bar-actions">
        <button class="action-btn">Back</button>
        <button class="action-btn action-btn--primary">Next: Plan</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ds-workspace-frame">
      <div class="workspace">
        <div class="workspace-sidebar">
          <div class="workspace-scroll">
            <section class="panel-section">
              <div class="section-header section-header--ruled"><h2 class="section-title">Folder</h2></div>
              <div class="panel-list">
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--muted"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="folder-open"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">thunder_blank/</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--muted"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="box"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">region/ · 12 .mca</span><span class="list-tag">2.4 MB</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--muted"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="file"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">level.dat</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--muted"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="file-x"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">map.xml</span><span class="badge badge--dim">absent</span></div>
              </div>
            </section>
            <section class="panel-section">
              <div class="section-header section-header--ruled"><h2 class="section-title">Already built</h2></div>
              <p class="section-desc">World features the scan found in the blocks — context for the phases ahead.</p>
              <div class="panel-list">
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--muted"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:var(--canvas-island)"></span><span class="list-label">Wool blocks</span><span class="list-tag">48</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--muted"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#5b8a4b"></span><span class="list-label">Resource blocks</span><span class="list-tag">120</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--muted"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="box"></i></span><span class="list-label">Chests</span><span class="list-tag">16</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--muted"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="dot"></i></span><span class="list-label">Spawners</span><span class="list-tag">0</span></div>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-handle"></div>
        <div class="workspace-canvas">
          <div class="canvas-subbar">
            <span class="canvas-cursor">Top-down · cleaned base</span>
            <div class="canvas-subbar-right">
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Fit island"><i data-lucide="maximize-2"></i></button>
              <span class="canvas-zoom">100%</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="canvas-surface canvas-surface--svg">
            <IslandMap Mode="neutral" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-handle"></div>
        <div class="workspace-inspector">
          <div class="workspace-scroll">
            <section class="panel-section">
              <div class="detail-header">
                <span class="geo-type-icon detail-icon--muted"><i data-lucide="sparkle"></i></span>
                <span class="detail-label">Detected</span>
                <span class="badge badge--success">ready to author</span>
              </div>
              <div class="section-body">
                <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Islands</label><div class="field-pick-row"><span class="badge badge--success">17</span><span class="list-tag">cleaned base</span></div></div>
                <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Symmetry</label><div class="field-pick-row"><span class="field-value">rot_90</span><span class="badge badge--success">100%</span></div></div>
                <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Suggested teams</label><div class="field-pick-row"><span class="badge badge--success">4</span><span class="list-tag">from rot_90</span></div></div>
                <p class="section-desc">Detection runs on the auto-cleaned base (ND2). You confirm all of this
                   in <strong>World</strong> → <strong>Teams</strong>; nothing here is final.</p>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  @* ── Sub-step 3 · Plan (no central canvas) ──────────────────────────────── *@
  <article class="ds-example">
    <div class="ds-example-label">Sub-step 3 of 3 — Plan (the six phases, then Start)</div>
    <div class="flow-bar">
      <div class="flow-bar-phase"><i data-lucide="import"></i><span>Import</span></div>
      <div class="flow-steps">
        <button class="flow-step flow-step--done"><i data-lucide="check"></i>Source</button>
        <button class="flow-step flow-step--done"><i data-lucide="check"></i>Found</button>
        <button class="flow-step flow-step--active">Plan</button>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-bar-actions">
        <button class="action-btn">Back</button>
        <button class="action-btn action-btn--primary"><i data-lucide="play"></i> Start authoring → Map Info</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ds-panel-frame">
      <div class="workspace-scroll">
        <section class="panel-section">
          <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
            <h2 class="section-title">Phases</h2>
            <span class="badge badge--dim">thunder_blank · 17 islands · rot_90</span>
          </div>
          <div class="section-body">
            <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot"></span><span class="step-label">0 · Map Info</span><span class="step-detail">Map name and authors. Version, mode, objective auto-derived.</span></div>
            <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot"></span><span class="step-label">1 · World</span><span class="step-detail">Scan · Islands · Symmetry — confirm the detection above. Seeds team count and spawn positions.</span></div>
            <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot"></span><span class="step-label">2 · Teams</span><span class="step-detail">Team creation + island assignment, then spawn point, then protection — defined once, orbit fills the rest.</span></div>
            <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot"></span><span class="step-label">3 · Build</span><span class="step-detail">Build height (side view) then the buildable layer of over-void bridges. The terrain is already buildable.</span></div>
            <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot"></span><span class="step-label">4 · Wools</span><span class="step-detail">Colours, then spawn, then monuments, then the room — one sub-step at a time; rules auto-wired.</span></div>
            <div class="step-row"><span class="step-dot"></span><span class="step-label">5 · Review</span><span class="step-detail">Round-trip · mirror-consistency · buildability · traversability gate — then export the XML.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="section-footer section-footer--separated">
            <div class="panel-warning">
              <strong>Build ⇄ Traversability is a loop.</strong> The closing gate is computed over the
              build / bridge geometry, so <em>build must precede wools</em>. If a spawn can't reach a wool,
              the gate sends you back to Build to add a bridge — it is not a separate step, it is the
              condition for export.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="section-footer">
            <span class="panel-save-status"><strong>Start authoring</strong> on the flow bar enters the wizard at Map Info.</span>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  </div>
</section>
